Bandicoot is written by a team of talented developers listed in the COPYRIGHTS.txt
file:

  ensmallen: a flexible C++ library for efficient function optimization.
  Copyright 2017-2023, Ryan Curtin <ryan@ratml.org>
  Copyright 2017-2023, Marcus Edel <marcus.edel@fu-berlin.de>
  Copyright 2017-2023, Conrad Sanderson

The RcppBandicoot package provides an integration of Bandicoot and its dependencies
into R. RcppBandicoot accomplishes this by linking into Rcpp,
establishing plugins, examples, and more. The R implementation was done by James
Joseph Balamuta with additional contributions by contributors listed in the ChangeLog.